high_descs: Turn right and walk  to the wall then turn right and walk to the trash.
Take the apple out of the trash.
Turn right and walk until you are even with the sink on your right and when you are turn right and walk to it.
Clean the apple in the sink then pick it back up and shut off the water.
Turn around and move forward about a foot then turn right and walk to the counter then turn right to face the small black table.
Put the clean apple on the black tables bottom right corner.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple on the table.

high_descs: Turn to your right twice so that you are facing the trash can
Pick up an apple from the trash can
Turn to your right twice so that you end up facing the sink
Put the apple in the sink and run the faucet for a few seconds, then pick the apple back up
Take a step to your left so that you face a small black table
Set the apple down on the black table
anns.task_desc: Pick up an apple, wash it and set it down on a table

high_descs: Turn right and then right again, and walk to the bin.
Take the yellow apple out of the bin.
Turn right and then veer right to the sink.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Take a step left and face the black table.
Place the apple on the front right corner of the table.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed apple on a table.
